  "id": "27777",
  "key": "DEV-5856",
  "summary": "AI Review Export Fails – \"Error generating PDF\" message displayed on History Panel and AI Review Screen",
  "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27777",
  "description": "*URL:-* [https://staging.awardedai.dev/review-proposal|https://staging.awardedai.dev/review-proposal]\n\n*Tested Server:-* Staging Environment.\n*Tested Version:-* App Version: 1.50.0\n\n+*Bug Description:*+\n\nWhen attempting to export AI Review results from either the History Panel or the AI Review screen, the export function fails and displays the message _\"Error generating PDF\"_. Please refer to the attached video for your reference.\n\n*Expected Result:*\nClicking the *Export* button should generate and download the PDF file of the AI Review report without any errors.\n\n*Actual Result:*\nAn error message _\"Error generating PDF\"_ is displayed, and the PDF file is not downloaded.\n\n+*Steps To Reproduce:-*+\n\n# Login with Valid credential.\n# Navigate to the *AI Review* screen.\n# Complete or select an existing AI Review result.\n# Click on the *Export* button.\n# Observe the message displayed.\n# Repeat the same process on the *History Panel* for an existing AI Review.\n\n+*Attached Video:-*+\n\n!AI Review Export.mp4|width=1280,height=680,alt=\"AI Review Export.mp4\"!",
